## Customize the voice

Puter.js supports multiple languages and voices. You can specify the language when calling the [txt2speech](https://docs.puter.com/AI/txt2speech/) function:

puter.ai.txt2speech("Bonjour, le monde\!", "fr-FR")  
    .then((audio) \=\> {  
        audio.play();  
    });
